{% schema %}
  {
    
    "name": "Section 2",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-568615017750987646 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/smooth-spine/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=568614436454007788&sectionId=568615017750987646)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvFTRsiEhf_text","label":"ggvFTRsiEhf_text","default":"How I Finally Fixed My (Morning) Pain and ‘Regained’ 9 Hours of Sleep In <span style=\"background-color:rgba(255,228,0,0.77);\">Less Than 7 Days</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggX4_f5toJx_text","label":"ggX4_f5toJx_text","default":"<p>Without invasive treatments, expensive physical therapy, or relying on harmful pills</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSRFFy-Soc_customText","label":"ggSRFFy-Soc_customText","default":"Rachel M. |"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKey2KlyRL_text","label":"ggKey2KlyRL_text","default":"<p>At 56 years old, I never thought <strong>I’d be nervous to go to sleep</strong>.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>But for the last 6 months, that’s exactly how it felt…</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Every night, I’d lay down on my side like I always had - only to wake up hours later <strong>with burning pain in my hip</strong>, a stiff lower back, and shooting <strong>cramps down my leg</strong>.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gguVSnF40Ak_youtubeUrl","label":"gguVSnF40Ak_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"gguVSnF40Ak_vimeoUrl","label":"gguVSnF40Ak_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"gguVSnF40Ak_html5Url","label":"gguVSnF40Ak_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/c96e78e38c2e426f92e9edf4dda4bc87.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggf3QwxbIIB_text","label":"ggf3QwxbIIB_text","default":"<p>At first, I chalked it up to aging…<br>&nbsp;</p><p>But when the pain started waking me up every 2 hours…</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And I needed my husband's help getting out of bed in the morning…</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>I knew something was completely wrong...</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQ0l5ooEf9_text","label":"ggQ0l5ooEf9_text","default":"My Life Had Become a Never Ending Nightmare"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7nt4zF8jQ_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg7nt4zF8jQ_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-1bc2ab13-1d13-401a-9d7e-342fee6d543e.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOksm2tNyK_text","label":"ggOksm2tNyK_text","default":"<p>I raised three kids and walked five miles a day into my late 50s.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>And I never minded getting my hands dirty in the garden.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But suddenly, everything became harder:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>I couldn’t stand for more than a few minutes</strong> without my hip flaring up.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Climbing the stairs felt like scaling a mountain.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I stopped walking with my neighbor in the mornings because I didn’t want to slow her down.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The worst part?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I started to feel like <strong>I was becoming dependent.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Like I was slowly watching my freedom - and my life - slip away.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Unable to enjoy what used to be my favourite activities.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXgtBAVWj3_text","label":"ggXgtBAVWj3_text","default":"I Tried Everything You’re “Supposed” to Try… Or So I Thought"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJtxi2zxja_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggJtxi2zxja_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-017cd110-db95-4d35-9a9d-6a7e7358522c.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gghL19RzZ1S_text","label":"gghL19RzZ1S_text","default":"<p>My first thought was that my mattress was too old.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>So I bought a brand-new one - medium-firm, memory foam, highly rated.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>No change.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Then I tried stretching before bed. Foam rolling. Heating pads.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Even physical therapy, twice a week for two months.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The therapist told me it was “normal wear and tear.”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>They gave me some exercises and sent me on my way.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7Oecj-hwj_youtubeUrl","label":"gg7Oecj-hwj_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7Oecj-hwj_vimeoUrl","label":"gg7Oecj-hwj_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7Oecj-hwj_html5Url","label":"gg7Oecj-hwj_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/980684b3ff09432ebd0d254edac64742.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmvc4TqCTS_text","label":"ggmvc4TqCTS_text","default":"<p><strong>But each morning, I kept waking up in pain.</strong><br>&nbsp;</p><p>And even worse, my mobility was getting worse day by day.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It terrified me.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I wasn’t ready to give up walking on my own.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I didn’t want to become one of those women who couldn’t go grocery shopping without help.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>And I refused to believe that this was “just part of getting older.”</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>So I went down the rabbit hole online, determined to find out what was really going on.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg912yBeZeE_text","label":"gg912yBeZeE_text","default":"The Real Root Cause Of My Back And Hip Pain&nbsp;"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAbXBpGJek_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggAbXBpGJek_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-52612e9e-33fb-4f8a-9400-21eb731ee9e3.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-E0zj8IYQ_text","label":"gg-E0zj8IYQ_text","default":"<p>One night I couldn’t sleep (again) and was aimlessly scrolling my phone.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>Then I saw a headline that stopped me cold.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It turns out, <strong>the thing no one talks about is what’s actually happening to your spine and hips when you sleep on your side.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>When I came across the term <strong>“Misalignment Lock”</strong>, something clicked.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It’s the position your body naturally shifts into when sleeping on your side - where your top leg pulls your spine out of alignment, rotates your hips, and slowly compresses the sciatic nerve.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzmIBO1Jpa_youtubeUrl","label":"ggzmIBO1Jpa_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzmIBO1Jpa_vimeoUrl","label":"ggzmIBO1Jpa_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzmIBO1Jpa_html5Url","label":"ggzmIBO1Jpa_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/c1b64e41bd8442e483ed3292ce555328.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOcyTXwgmg_text","label":"ggOcyTXwgmg_text","default":"<p>It’s not something you can feel happening in the moment.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</p><p>But hour after hour - night after night - it builds up.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Until suddenly <strong>you’re waking up with searing pain, lower back stiffness, or even signs of sciatica.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And here’s the kicker:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>No mattress, back sleeping trick, or “regular” pillow fixes it</strong> - because they don’t actually support your top leg or correct your alignment while you sleep.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I couldn’t believe something so simple could be doing this much damage every night.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And the video claimed <strong>there was a solution made specifically to stop it.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggluNG2XzlS_text","label":"ggluNG2XzlS_text","default":"Not Your Ordinary Solution, Backed by Science"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTQtEIPwIR_youtubeUrl","label":"ggTQtEIPwIR_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTQtEIPwIR_vimeoUrl","label":"ggTQtEIPwIR_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTQtEIPwIR_html5Url","label":"ggTQtEIPwIR_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/98c43a8309fb4182a28c49a4a78091fb.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggl6IFgAKrk_text","label":"ggl6IFgAKrk_text","default":"<p>The video introduced a product called the SmoothSpine™ Alignment Pillow - and right away, I could tell <strong>this wasn’t like anything I had tried.</strong>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</p><p>It didn’t look like a regular leg pillow.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It was contoured, structured, and <strong>had a soft, built-in strap</strong> that keeps it from shifting during the night.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But what really caught my attention was how it worked…</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The SmoothSpine Pillow uses something called: <strong>“Active Spine Realignment™”</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>A breakthrough support system <strong>developed by physiotherapists that corrects your sleep posture</strong>, stabilizes your hips, and keeps your spine perfectly aligned while you sleep on your side.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggz5GlnAJTM_text","label":"ggz5GlnAJTM_text","default":"<p><strong>The 4 key changes it makes from night one:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>1.</strong> <strong>Lifts your top leg</strong> so your hips stay level</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>2.</strong> <strong>Prevents your spine</strong> from twisting or rotating</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>3.</strong> Takes pressure off the sciatic nerve <strong>to stop that burning, shooting pain</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>4. Stays in place all night</strong> - no shifting, sliding, or collapsing</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPh6RhKUHj_youtubeUrl","label":"ggPh6RhKUHj_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPh6RhKUHj_vimeoUrl","label":"ggPh6RhKUHj_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPh6RhKUHj_html5Url","label":"ggPh6RhKUHj_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/495a61674ab34198b8fade42692accb2.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggokUTyl6M1_text","label":"ggokUTyl6M1_text","default":"<p>It sounded simple - and almost too good to be true.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>But the reviews?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Over 57,000 people had already used it, and the company was offering a 90-night money-back guarantee.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>At that point, I figured: what do I have to lose?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggiIJe69Rjo_text","label":"ggiIJe69Rjo_text","default":"I Ordered My Own SmoothSpine Pillow Right Then And There"},{"type":"html","id":"ggefRUrDU56_youtubeUrl","label":"ggefRUrDU56_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggefRUrDU56_vimeoUrl","label":"ggefRUrDU56_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggefRUrDU56_html5Url","label":"ggefRUrDU56_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/9d23f710552647f9843288c369b8ceae.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAkZDP2hHW_text","label":"ggAkZDP2hHW_text","default":"<p>It arrived just a few days later - neatly packaged in a sturdy travel bag.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>That first night, I followed the simple instructions, placed the pillow between my legs, and slid the strap around my thigh.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>It felt secure… supportive… and oddly comforting.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I didn’t expect much.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>But what happened next truly shocked me…</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVWTdgbm0H_text","label":"ggVWTdgbm0H_text","default":"My Honest Experience After 14 Nights Of Sleep"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNY422wyrh_youtubeUrl","label":"ggNY422wyrh_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNY422wyrh_vimeoUrl","label":"ggNY422wyrh_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNY422wyrh_html5Url","label":"ggNY422wyrh_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/69cf0b74040c49ae9ea571570077d30b.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCrJm6zHQy_label","label":"ggCrJm6zHQy_label","default":"<p>Night 1:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6sZSk6gMV_text","label":"gg6sZSk6gMV_text","default":"<p>I still woke up once or twice, but when I stood up that morning, something was… easier.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>There wasn’t that usual tightness that made me pause at the edge of the bed.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>My back didn’t feel locked up.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I walked to the bathroom without wincing or bracing myself.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVDDAQD4fA_label","label":"ggVDDAQD4fA_label","default":"<p>Night 3:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrTon08aDs_text","label":"ggrTon08aDs_text","default":"<p><strong>I noticed I was sleeping deeper.</strong><br>&nbsp;</p><p>I didn’t wake up to shift positions like I usually did.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And for the first time in months, I didn’t reach for my morning pain cream.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I got dressed, made breakfast, and felt steady on my feet. That was a big deal for me.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrgqdVmkHg_label","label":"ggrgqdVmkHg_label","default":"<p>Night 7:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggi7Yc08Xs8_text","label":"ggi7Yc08Xs8_text","default":"<p>I realized I hadn’t needed help getting out of bed all week.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>My balance was better. My movements felt more fluid.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Even my posture while standing seemed to have improved.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>I told my husband, “I think this thing is actually working.”</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>He smiled and said, “You’ve been sleeping through the night. I noticed.”</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggquE0QL4aq_label","label":"ggquE0QL4aq_label","default":"<p>Week 2:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggiKerermPT_text","label":"ggiKerermPT_text","default":"<p>I walked the full loop around our neighborhood, twice, without that sharp pain that used to show up halfway through.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>I was doing things I hadn’t done in months:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Gardening for longer periods, shopping without needing to lean on the cart, and even rode in the car for 3 hours to visit my daughter, pain-free.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I felt more like myself again.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>And all I had done was support my spine the right way while I slept.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggm4JuZV5_W_text","label":"ggm4JuZV5_W_text","default":"Final Thoughts (And Why I’m Writing This)"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYvn-FlP0E_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggYvn-FlP0E_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-ce79c43c-84ac-49ca-9a90-0127d408d66b.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gglrQTX_5CM_text","label":"gglrQTX_5CM_text","default":"<p>If you’re anything like I was…<br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>A side sleeper struggling with hip pain, lower back tension, or sciatic nerve flare-ups, and you’ve tried everything from fancy mattresses to stretches, but nothing sticks…</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Then please hear me when I say this:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It isn’t your mattress.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It isn’t your posture.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggC1S73nPH7_text","label":"ggC1S73nPH7_text","default":"It is your spinal alignment during sleep."},{"type":"html","id":"gg7XL8mL6AC_text","label":"gg7XL8mL6AC_text","default":"<p>The SmoothSpine Pillow fixed something I didn’t even know was broken.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>And <strong>it gave me back my mornings, my sleep, my energy</strong> - and honestly, my love for living life.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I’ve since bought a second one for travel.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Last time I ordered, <strong>there was very limited stock</strong> so I’d check and see if they’re still available.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If they are, I highly recommend buying a few pillows at least!&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>You don’t have to keep on dragging through life deprived of genuine recovery.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>You can change all of that today. <strong>Give this a try and get RID of the pain. You can thank me later.&nbsp;</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsyXpBQsiT_text","label":"ggsyXpBQsiT_text","default":"<p><strong>A Special Offer for Our Readers:</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Claim Your SmoothSpine Pillow Now and <strong>SAVE 60% OFF</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Take advantage of our discount link by clicking below!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYQWWuZDAe_label","label":"ggYQWWuZDAe_label","default":"<p>Apply Discount &amp; Check Availability</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggM1bz3-9Al_text","label":"ggM1bz3-9Al_text","default":"<p><strong>Note:</strong> Offer Not Available on Amazon Or eBay</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggm1CpQzLbl_text","label":"ggm1CpQzLbl_text","default":"What Are People Saying About The SmoothSpine Pillow?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCrFeXtw36_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggCrFeXtw36_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-cb5f87ef-bbf9-40fa-a100-141946a4fb73.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPZYtTlG3x_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggPZYtTlG3x_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-5177da4b-16e3-42fd-aa02-408bebb2c072.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRQo6qLzDv_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggRQo6qLzDv_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-5177da4b-16e3-42fd-aa02-408bebb2c072.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRQo6qLzDv_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggRQo6qLzDv_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-59d65c5d-2422-44bf-9deb-ddd38083c961.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2Aet_zgzl_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg2Aet_zgzl_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-3017b1b0-2b34-4229-a09f-5499df679f31.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMEF-gxYfx_srcS